window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Fatherhood is a painful profession in the Brickborn family.</p> <p>When a long-forgotten book finds its way into the hands of Mullentide’s most magical family, Alden’s epic journey home begins. What was meant to be a tool to save the innocent from being sacrificed backfires. Fire, blood, and vengeance will flow as Alden is ripped away from his family by a madman desperate to fulfill a centuries-old plot. Enter a brutal fantasy world of magic, vicious monsters, and friendships forged in hardship.</p> <p>When doing what’s right threatens to take everything from him, what will Alden sacrifice to see his wife and daughter again?</p>"; 
